<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Deployment erfolgreich</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: #212529;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .status-banner {
            background: #198754;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .status-banner .icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #212529;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            width: 140px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #212529;
        }
        .commit-box {
            background: #e7f5ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0d6efd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .commit-hash {
            font-family: 'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;
            background: #dee2e6;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background-color: #0d6efd;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Dployr</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="status-banner">
                &#10003; Deployment erfolgreich
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Hallo <%= username %>,</h2>
                <p>Dein Projekt wurde erfolgreich aktualisiert!</p>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">Projekt:</span>
                        <span class="info-value"><strong><%= projectName %></strong></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">Ausl√∂ser:</span>
                        <span class="info-value"><%= triggerType %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">Dauer:</span>
                        <span class="info-value"><%= duration %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">Zeitpunkt:</span>
                        <span class="info-value"><%= timestamp %></span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <% if (commitMessage) { %>
                <div class="commit-box">
                    <strong>Letzter Commit:</strong><br>
                    <span class="commit-hash"><%= newCommit %></span> - <%= commitMessage %>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="<%= projectUrl %>" class="button">Projekt ansehen</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Diese E-Mail wurde automatisch gesendet. Bitte antworte nicht darauf.</p>
                <p><a href="<%= settingsUrl %>">Benachrichtigungseinstellungen anpassen</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
